---
import LockIcon from "../icons/LockIcon.astro";
---
<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-32">
                    <div
                        class="relative rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-500/10 to-transparent border border-amber-500/20 p-8 md:p-12 overflow-hidden">
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-amber-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"/>

                        <div class="relative">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                                <div
                                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/20 border border-amber-500/30 text-amber-400">
                                    <LockIcon/>
                                </div>
                                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-100">
                                    Security built into the proxy layer
                                </h2>
                            </div>

                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mb-3">Authentication</h3>
                                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-zinc-400">
                                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                            <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                                            <span>API keys with bcrypt hashing, prefix lookup, automatic expiration</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                            <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                                            <span>JWT/OIDC integration with JWKS validation and SSO support</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                            <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                                            <span>Identity propagation: track callers from HTTP header to audit log</span>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mb-3">Hardening</h3>
                                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-zinc-400">
                                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                            <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                                            <span>Agent TLS with custom CA and mTLS support</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                            <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                                            <span>Tool access filtering with allow/deny lists and glob patterns</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                            <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                                            <span>Capability declaration and runtime verification</span>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
